title: Blue Beetle is the Best DC Film of the Year
description:
This video is sponsored by Trade. Trade is offering my viewers a free bag of coffee with any subscription at http://www.drinktrade.com/captainmidnight
DC Studio's new Blue Beetle is a fun addition to their line-up and their best film of the year, but is that enough? In this video I go over the highs and lows of Jamie Reyes' first adventure.
